@@ -0,0 +1,28 @@
+## @file
+#  Cpu MM driver specific declarations.
+#
+#  This file defines Guids and declares Pcd values for Cpu MM driver.
+#
+#  Copyright (c) 2021 - 2022, ARM Limited. All rights reserved.
+#
